const sourceCode = "# Export Reports\n\nExport scan results as PDF or Excel for sharing with stakeholders.\n\n## PDF Report\n\nA formatted document with:\n\n- **Executive summary** — AI-generated narrative overview\n- **Score gauge** and key metrics\n- **Issue breakdown** by severity\n- **Full issue list** with descriptions, selectors, and fix suggestions\n- **Page screenshot** with issue highlights\n\n## Excel Spreadsheet\n\nA multi-sheet workbook with:\n\n- **Summary sheet** — score, scan metadata, top priorities\n- **Issues sheet** — filterable table of all issues with every field\n- **Positive findings** — what the page does well\n\n## How to Export\n\n### Single-Page Scan\n\nFrom the scan results page, click the **Export** dropdown and choose PDF or Excel.\n\n### API\n\n```bash\n# PDF\ncurl -o report.pdf \\\n  \"http://localhost:3000/api/scans/{scanId}/export?format=pdf\"\n\n# Excel\ncurl -o report.xlsx \\\n  \"http://localhost:3000/api/scans/{scanId}/export?format=excel\"\n```\n\n## Notes\n\n- Export is only available for completed scans (`completed` or `completed_partial`)\n- The PDF executive summary is generated by AI on-the-fly — there may be a brief delay\n- Excel files include all issue fields for maximum filterability";
